# ==========================================
# CLI Clipper - Environment Variables
# ==========================================

# GitHub Configuration
# Your GitHub username or organization name
GITHUB_OWNER=your-username

# Repository name for the GitHub Actions workflow
GITHUB_REPO=clipper-actions

# GitHub Personal Access Token with repo and workflow scopes
# Create at: https://github.com/settings/tokens
GH_PAT=ghp_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# ==========================================
# AI Services - API Key Rotation
# ==========================================

# API Key Rotation Setup:
# The system supports multiple API keys per service with automatic round-robin rotation.
# This helps distribute load across multiple keys and avoid rate limits.
#
# Option 1: Use Environment Variables (Single Key)
#   - Set DEEPGRAM_API_KEY and GEMINI_API_KEY below
#   - Useful for development or single-key setups
#
# Option 2: Use Key Files (Multiple Keys with Rotation)
#   - Create config/keys/deepgram-keys.txt with one Deepgram API key per line
#   - Create config/keys/gemini-keys.txt with one Gemini API key per line
#   - Copy the example files:
#     - cp config/keys/deepgram-keys.example config/keys/deepgram-keys.txt
#     - cp config/keys/gemini-keys.example config/keys/gemini-keys.txt
#   - The system will automatically rotate through keys
#
# Priority: Key files (if they exist) > Environment variables
#
# Get your keys:
# - Deepgram: https://console.deepgram.com
# - Gemini: https://ai.google.dev

# Deepgram API Key for speech-to-text transcription
# Fallback (used only if config/keys/deepgram-keys.txt doesn't exist)
DEEPGRAM_API_KEY=xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# Google Gemini API Key for viral moment analysis
# Fallback (used only if config/keys/gemini-keys.txt doesn't exist)
GEMINI_API_KEY=AIzaSyxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# ==========================================
# Telegram Bot (Optional)
# ==========================================

# Telegram Bot Token from @BotFather
# 1. Message @BotFather on Telegram
# 2. Send /newbot and follow instructions
# 3. Copy the token
TELEGRAM_TOKEN=123456789:ABCdefGHIjklMNOpqrsTUVwxyz

# Your Telegram Chat ID to receive videos
# 1. Message @userinfobot on Telegram
# 2. Copy your Chat ID (may start with -100 for groups)
CHAT_ID=-1001234567890
